Description:
delete a metric heading

Usage: delete_metric_table_heading [-help]
                                   [-format {html excel text}] -id <string>

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-format {html excel text}     # config for specified report_metric format
                              # (enum, optional)
-id <string>                  # id of the heading to be deleted
                              # (string, required)